            <title>[SOLR-16210] Lift Configuration Change to Correct failing Lift Tools</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-16210</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently many of the tools provided by lift are not functioning because lift is unable to complete compilation. There is a bug on the lift side that should be fixed soon, but in addition there is an issue caused by AntoraSite. To work around the AntoraSite failure I recommend disabling in via lift toml.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I will submit a pr to do this. Thanks much for your patience and hard work on Solr&lt;/p&gt;</description>
